A 50-minute timer has been added to restart before it gets stuck.

It can be modified in the main.cpp:


#if defined(ESP8266)
  l_info(TAG_MAIN, "ESP8266 - Disable WDT");
  ESP.wdtDisable();
  *((volatile uint32_t *)0x60000900) &= ~(1);
  restartTimer.attach(x, restartESP); // Restart every x seconds
#else
